Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门湾悲剧随光芒溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼焦视网膜的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木驱使着GUNDAM1号机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与2号机展开最后之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为将宿命打上休止符而被牵引在一起的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗无止尽地持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但浦木并不知道那只是“星尘”的序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架GUNDAM消失于所罗门之海时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星尘”终于显露出其真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹阁下的舰队由左舷接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将会合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达各舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行对希玛舰队的补给作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼前浮现着贾布罗慌乱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，会回以什么答复呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，不管如何答复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘作战的目标是不会变更的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭已射出了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹怎么会接受这种要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且即使在月球扔下了殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也丝毫动摇不了联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不管其真正用意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对目前政局造成不良影响…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想维持政权吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就月球的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都有一致的认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫平民统治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，对新的阻碍者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克西斯来的舰队该如何处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持中立的话允许他们有期限地停留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要特地与之为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在向月球移动的殖民地在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这是金米岛的残存舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大战速的舰队能在殖民地坠落前捕捉到敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将殖民地移动用推进燃料点燃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的意图就挫败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫荡海盗也就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在劫持殖民地时为何不使用推进燃料呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还特地用殖民地相撞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为没有足以点燃的能量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙还是安静点好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0068,,{\fs38}阿克西斯先遣舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们的作战感佩之至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也非常渴望能尽量加以协助啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了这中立的阿克西斯舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才能无后顾之忧地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事成之后士兵的回收请务必…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我可以发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿克西斯一点小小的饯行礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是ZION精神的实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是MA“Neue Ziel”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Neue Ziel：型号AMX-002 阿克西斯制造的宇宙战用试作型重MA\N机体上装有I FIELD发生器，使敌方光束武器攻击无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目测“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离8000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光传感器开放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始导航
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉冲照射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接前10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航光正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度11
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要接收3号机了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？闷闷不乐的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上陆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜仍然反对我驾驶3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行系留作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿纳海姆最大的舰只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合做3号机的测试基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备接驳舷梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说宏，3号机是怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实体只有妮娜和舰长知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是什么宇宙空间据点防卫用的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据点防卫用？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的驾驶员就是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是401警戒中队的纳卡哈·中门少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你是GUNDAM的机师也告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂在入港期间将纳入本中队的管理之下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除阿尔比昂追击迪拉兹舰队的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新任务是担任“玫瑰人生”及GUNDAM3号机的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请、请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点接收3号机并阻止坠落的殖民地的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地交给金米岛的追击舰队就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们得到了高云将军非正式允诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM开发计划已不再由高云将军管辖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成这样的理由你们也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号机被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阅舰式被搞得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉为递交战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能与我同行“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上陆的只限舰长和妮娜·巴普尔顿还有他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦还真一本正经地答复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到阿克西斯先遣舰队认可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就达到目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛在行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正照预定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来“玫瑰人生”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是所长克蕾娜·哈克谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿尔比昂舰长席那普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了，所长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能让其他人一起上陆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已见过中门少佐了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是负责GUNDAM3号机开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是露雪特·奥德比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你精神很好呢，露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说1号机的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉，我听说过你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你也精通MS理论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必担任3号机的试飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划已暂时中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能让他驾驶3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号机已经完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下修正实用方面的数据而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须执行命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上就是中止开发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，军方到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中门少佐一到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把测试人员遣回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开发1号机的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能了解我的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有测试机师的话研究也无法继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是完美的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的话一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浦木中尉让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的瞬间的机动判断力、未来预测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是能在理解机械的情况下操作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话就算是3号机复杂的武器管理系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用得着那么生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已赶不上战局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是失去了1号机而失常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了，是殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与本队联络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先锋军已捕捉到敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗配置，进入炮击战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方11时角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高热源体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉没吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，中门少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱、抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打扰一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有东西要给中尉看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我？难道是3号机？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是数据大多被中门少佐接管了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在手上只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信，这全部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？能驾驶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要取得3号机就看你的决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是违反命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不正是需要3号机之时吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这是为的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人也会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保卫联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的好答复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉已经接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一定要这么拼命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里磨蹭的话卡多他们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经上了月球的绕行轨道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的救命稻草的联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在卡多面前束手束脚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始调整镜面角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开起爆聚光器的回路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想把殖民地扔到月球上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才教你解救冯·布朗的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，只剩下两条路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被殖民地压得上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地获得推力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将殖民地移动用的推进燃料点燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会、会往哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到推力的殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离月球绕行轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，这回会被地球引力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地坠落的真正目标是地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会是一年战争悲剧的重演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离地球还有38小时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么要佯攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，是要让追击舰队耗尽推进燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间犹豫了，浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是玛德拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们推进燃料用尽，无法续航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是蒙哥列
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推力下降，脱离阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生，这样下去还能剩几艘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给舰何时才能到达？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，阿尔比昂的机师到工场区去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他揪出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他碰到3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抵抗的话，准许开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机正好啊，中尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…并不是Core Block System
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Core Block System：核心操作舱系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…那个尾翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也兼做连接系统的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，详情稍后再谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了，浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是在做什么？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，离开GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在吓唬人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉，快进驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来，现在还可以不问罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你对现状的判断吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把平民当做盾牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且杀害平民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就该受军法会议处分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我代为行刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子塞住的混蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点扔掉枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，嫁祸于人太不识趣了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙几时…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请撤掉士兵，中门少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人应该是迪拉兹舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，你来照料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生，快叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请照顾好3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始就已知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反对3号机的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我和宏的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你并不只是在担心他的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生，快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在3年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球…3年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和卡多大尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往过的事我都知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不愿再见到他们两人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号机…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将3号机…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请祝福露雪特·奥德比
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能叫做MS吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换自动的时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看赋值监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲内柜的武器载入要在3秒以内
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟随而来的敌人也到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.05,0:25:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但数据里并没有这家伙

Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.11,0:27:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.94,0:27:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止界限点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.58,0:27:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是能防止殖民地坠落的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.98,0:28:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止界限点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越过此处人将无法改变命运
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.34,0:28:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM3号机
